{"tid":1118467,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片]RDJ 親自解析《Avengers: Endgame》：「片尾 8 分鐘為 Marvel 歷史最棒！」","createTime":"2019-04-21T12:29:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T13:34:25.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ace8572f1d9206451217519ae8d7eaf8d59c2558","tid":1118467,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:29:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PKNIjmlmN4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPKNIjmlmN4s&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RCpZd1NrJsyKidS%2BVLva3MM%3D&h=fed748ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PKNIjmlmN4s</a><br />\n<br />\n距離《Avengers: Endgame》上映不到一星期，網絡上不少新聞焦點都著重在此片的話題，例如早前曾為大家報導有網民將 MCU 所有電影濃縮，打造成 20 分鐘的回顧短片。近日忙於海外進行宣傳的「Iron Man」Robert Downey Jr. 與 The Upcoming 的專訪中，親自透露了《Avengers: Endgame》最後片尾 8 分鐘為 Marvel 電影歷史最棒，因為大家皆參與其中。<br />\n<br />\nThe last eight minutes of that movie are maybe the best eight minutes in the entire history of the whole run of them, in a way, because everyone&rsquo;s involved<br />\n<br />\n而 Robert Downey Jr. 所說的「大家」包含了誰，此話可謂意味深長，外界猜測將有不少新的英雄投入本場戰局，相信下周等待正片上映，所有真相就能水落石出。<br />\n<br />\n此外，Robert Downey Jr. 也簡單談論了《Avengers: Endgame》這部片所代表的重大意義，有興趣的讀者不妨撥空觀看上方影片，亦可關注《Avengers: Endgame》藝術家創作電影海報釋出情報。"},{"pid":"72e88b17939aaf357b0aadab6b189238dd25236c","tid":1118467,"uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:31:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2019/4/avengers-endgame-robert-downey-jr-final-eight-minutes-best-mcu-marvel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2019%2F4%2Favengers-endgame-robert-downey-jr-final-eight-minutes-best-mcu-marvel&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RCpZd1NrJsyKidS%2BVLva3MM%3D&h=e580ba5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2019/4/avengers-endgame-robert-downey-jr-final-eight-minutes-best-mcu-marvel</a>"},{"pid":"701cd7ad2f0f48a0eefa7967d872a0c8b69899c9","t